Author: NEWBOLD
Vol / Page: 30
Edition:
Quote: But when he said `gidday mate' to the magistrate . . . they . . . just remanded him straight out to the wow. <i>Ibid.</i> 255 WOW (n) Mental asylum. Originates from Maori `Whau', the name of the Auckland river next to which Oakley Mental Hospital is situated
